{"serial": "61007", "department_serial": 56, "code": "AP2039", "class": "*", "name": {"en": "Atmospheric Instrumentation and Observation Ⅰ", "ch": "大氣測計及操作Ⅰ"}, "notice": {"en": "", "ch": ""}, "instructor": {"en": ["Chang, Wei-Yu"], "ch": ["張偉裕"]}, "credits": 3, "time_loc": [{"time": {"week": 1, "session": ["5", "6"]}, "loc": {"building": "S1", "room": "625"}}, {"time": {"week": 2, "session": ["1"]}, "loc": {"building": "S1", "room": "713"}}, {"time": {"week": 2, "session": ["2"]}, "loc": {"building": "S1", "room": "716"}}], "isRequired": true, "isFullSem": false, "MaxStu": 60, "department": {"ch": "大氣科學學系", "en": "Department of Atmospheric Physics"}, "system": {"ch": "學士班", "en": "Undergraduate Programme"}, "language": {"ch": "國語", "en": "Chinese"}, "card": {"ch": "部份使用", "en": "Optional"}, "assigned": 0, "selected": 30, "remark": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "goal": {"ch": "1.了解大氣測計的基本概念與觀測資料之特性與應用。\n2.了解地面氣象觀測之儀器特性、觀測原理與應用。\n3.了解高空觀測之儀器特性、觀測原理與應用。\n4.了解雷達與衛星等大氣遙測之基礎原理及遙測影像之分析與應用。\n5.了解其他特種大氣觀測之儀器與觀測方法。", "en": "1. To understand the basic concept of atmospheric observation data and characteristics/applications of observational data. \n2. To understand the characteristics of ground-based meteorological instrument, measuring principle and its applications. \n3. To understand the characteristics of high-altitude meteorological instrument, measuring principle and its applications. \n4. To understand the concepts of remote sensing instruments (radar and satellite). \n5. To understand the other special meteorological instrument."}, "outline": {"ch": "臺灣氣象觀測介紹\n中大測站參觀與測量\n單位與量測準確度、Design thinking\n天氣現象與編碼(含地面狀態)\n雲\n能見度\n大氣壓力\n板橋探空站參訪\n風\n溫度\n溼度\n降水\n大氣輻射與日照\n野外教室教學", "en": "Introducing meteorological observations in Taiwan\nVisiting NCU meteorological station\nUnits, measuring accuracy, design thinking\nMeteorological phenomena and weather code\nCloud\nVisibility\nAtmospheric pressure\nVisiting Taipei sounding station\nWind\nTemperature\nHumidity\nPrecipitation\nAtmospheric radiation"}, "textbook": {"ch": "1.氣 象 測 報 手 冊，中 央 氣 象 局，2004。\n2.The Weather Observer’s Handbook, Stephen Burt, 2012. (圖書館電子書下載)\n3.Guide to Meteorological Instruments and Methods of Observation (8th Edition), WMO, 2008. (網路搜尋下載)\n4.大 氣 測 計 學 (第 二 版)， 劉 明 揚，2011。\n5.氣 象 電 碼 手 冊，中 央 氣 象 局，1986。", "en": "1.The Weather Observer’s Handbook, Stephen Burt, 2012. (圖書館電子書下載)\n2.Guide to Meteorological Instruments and Methods of Observation (8th Edition), WMO, 2008. (網路搜尋下載)"}, "selfCompiledRate": {"ch": "30", "en": "30"}, "instructMethod": {"ch": "講授", "en": ["Lecture"]}, "gradMethod": {"ch": "個人作業 40％、期中考 30％、期末考 30％", "en": "homework 35％, mid-term 30％, final-exam 35％"}, "officeHour": {"ch": "週一10~12am", "en": "Monday 10-12 am"}, "teachWeeks": {"ch": "18", "en": "18"}, "flexDiscription": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "domain": {"ch": "基礎學科(大氣組)", "en": "基礎學科(大氣組)"}, "map": {"ch": [{"competencies": "數理基礎能力", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習"]}, {"competencies": "專業知識能力", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習"]}, {"competencies": "資訊應用能力", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習"]}, {"competencies": "國際視野與語文溝通能力", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習"]}, {"competencies": "獨立思考能力", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習"]}, {"competencies": "專業倫理及服務學習之能力", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習"]}], "en": [{"competencies": "Ability in basic mathematics and science", "rating": "(4)High", "assesments": ["Test/Exam", "Assignments"]}, {"competencies": "Ability in professional knowledge", "rating": "(4)High", "assesments": ["Test/Exam", "Assignments"]}, {"competencies": "Ability in information applications", "rating": "(4)High", "assesments": ["Test/Exam", "Assignments"]}, {"competencies": "Ability in international horizons and communication", "rating": "(4)High", "assesments": ["Test/Exam", "Assignments"]}, {"competencies": "Ability in independent thinking", "rating": "(4)High", "assesments": ["Test/Exam", "Assignmen